my as one of the Straw Hats and as a former bounty hunter, Zoro is also regarded as one of twelve pirates who are referred to as the \"Worst Generation\".</p>\n<p>He currently has a bounty of Beli.png320,000,000.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"zoro"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1003640200","426988268","893747738"]}